{"tid":1956594,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"最新：人行定向降準一個百分點 料釋放4000億人民幣","createTime":"2020-04-03T09:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T12:56:33.000Z","uid":30040,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"e160c530273585400c1c485af6efab01014a9e79","tid":1956594,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"最新：人行定向降準一個百分點 料釋放4000億人民幣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cupr2Oz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCupr2Oz.png&h=6099d836&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de09a53b4c5ec5d9eb609fac56ef71a3779cf947","tid":1956594,"uid":289946,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"Gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0004ebc7945abfa17ab4643f4fc7d03c540602d","tid":1956594,"uid":30040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"【人行對中小銀行定向降準 釋放4000億】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wXcRNS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wXcRNS&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=b6bd4f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2wXcRNS</a><br />\n<br />\n#中國人民銀行 宣布，對中小銀行定向降準。<br />\n<br />\n人行表示，為支持實體經濟發展，促進加大對中小微企業的支持力度，降低社會融資實際成本，人行決定對農村信用社、農村商業銀行、農村合作銀行、村鎮銀行和僅在省級行政區域內經營的城市商業銀行定向下調存款準備金率1個百分點，於4月15日和5月15日分兩次實施到位，每次下調0.5個百分點，共釋放長期資金約4000億元。<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n最新 📣📣《信報》+《信報月刊》訂閱優惠<br />\n了解更多：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/ejfdncom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fejfdncom&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=3eb704f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/ejfdncom</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #即時新聞"},{"pid":"44ac2e5498685a3f325eed0608a07c39d7312756","tid":1956594,"uid":53853,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"de09a53b4c5ec5d9eb609fac56ef71a3779cf947","tid":1956594,"uid":289946,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"rep